For {= country =}+ African countries, cover each of the {= support_role =} support roles listed below with at least {= country_support_role_actor =}+ named public support actors or programs per country-role cell; for each (`country`, `support_role`, `actor`) combination, supply an actor/program-scoped public source (i.e. {= url =}+ URL) showing the actor/program, the country or market tie, the support role, and the impact / small-and-growing-business / social-enterprise relevance.

This is public ecosystem-infrastructure provenance, not a startup ranking, funding tracker, investment screen, grant-application guide, contact list, outreach workflow, lead score, dashboard, alert, or strategy recommendation.

